comments: Sabonis (SAC) grasps and then quickly releases Gobert's (MIN) left arm during the rebound.
Sabonis (SAC) engages with Gobert (MIN) after the release of the jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs as Gobert back-taps the ball toward the perimeter during the rebound.
McDaniels (MIN) is moving over the pick when marginal contact occurs with Monk's (SAC) right leg during the drive.
Gobert (MIN) slightly extends forward prior to marginal body contact occurring with Monk (SAC) during Monk's driving shot attempt.
Barnes (SAC) and Gobert (MIN) make incidental arm contact with one another as they each pursue the rebound.
Towns (MIN) grasps and then quickly releases Sabonis' (SAC) right arm as he crashes toward the ball during the rebound.
Sabonis (SAC) is firming up over his left foot in McDaniels' (MIN) path following the hand-off and does not deliver illegal contact during the pick.

Gobert (MIN) is turning with his left forearm brought forward slightly when marginal contact occurs with Sabonis' (SAC) right side during Sabonis' upward shooting motion. Gobert then cleanly blocks the layup attempt.
Gobert (MIN) re-establishes in bounds prior to back-tapping the ball during the rebound.
Sabonis (SAC) and Gobert (MIN) engage and disengage with one another as the entry pass into the lane is made.
Sabonis (SAC) initiates contact with Gobert's (MIN) right side and arm as Gobert starts his upward shooting motion.
Towns (MIN) slightly extends his left arm forward prior to marginal contact occurring with Barnes' (SAC) right side at the end of the drive and as Barnes gathers the ball.
Sabonis (SAC) brings his left hand toward Gobert's (MIN) back and marginal contact occurs as they each attempt to establish rebounding position.
Sabonis (SAC) and Reid (MIN) make incidental arm contact with one another as they each elevate for the rebound.
Sabonis' (SAC) left leg is slightly extending outward as he establishes his screening position in Conley's (MIN) path and marginal contact occurs as Sabonis sets the pick following the hand-off.
Sabonis (SAC) and Conley (MIN) come together at the same spot off-ball and incidental contact occurs as the pass is made.

Replay review of the foul called on Conley (MIN) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Conley initiates contact with Sabonis' (SAC) right arm that affects Sabonis' ability to pursue the rebound.
Reid (MIN) legally contests Monk's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Huerter (SAC) and McDaniels (MIN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Barnes (SAC) and Towns (MIN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Gobert (MIN) re-establishes slightly in Lyles' (SAC) path following the initial contact during the screen and further marginal contact occurs as Lyles attempts to move around the screen.
Barnes (SAC) and Lyles (SAC) each legally contest Towns' (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Correctly called shot clock violation on Sacramento. The game clock is reset to 00:02.9.
Reid (MIN) fumbles the ball after receiving the pass, gathers it, and legally starts his dribble thereafter.
Lyles (SAC) jumps alongside Reid (MIN) and cleanly blocks the shot attempt as simultaneous incidental contact occurs.
McDaniels (MIN) shuffles somewhat laterally prior to marginal body contact occurring with Monk (SAC) during Monk's drive.
Conley (MIN) slightly extends toward Monk's (SAC) path prior to marginal body contact occurring at the end of Monk's drive.
Barnes (SAC) makes clean contact with the ball as simultaneous marginal contact occurs with Gobert's (MIN) back as Gobert jumps from underneath the basket during his upward shooting motion.
McDaniels (MIN) and Lyles (SAC) engage and disengage with one another as they each attempt to establish rebounding position, and marginal contact occurs prior to Lyles back-tapping the ball.
Gobert (MIN) brings his left hand forward toward Monk's (SAC) front and marginal contact occurs after Monk mishandles the ball during the drive.
McDaniels (MIN) initiates contact with Monk's (SAC) head during the driving shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Reid (MIN) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Conley (MIN) and Huerter (SAC) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Huerter's (SAC) hands and right leg slightly extend forward prior to marginal contact occurring with McDaniels' (MIN) side and left leg during the pick.
Lyles (SAC) establishes himself in McDaniels' (MIN) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the pick.
Towns (MIN) contests Huerter's (SAC) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Barnes (SAC) brings his hand toward Towns' (MIN) front and marginal contact occurs as Towns makes the pass.
Huerter (SAC) legally contests Reid's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Towns (MIN) commits a take foul on Lyles (SAC). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Monk's (SAC) left arm slides across Conley's (MIN) front and marginal contact occurs as Conley dribbles in transition.
Lyles (SAC) legally contests Conley's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
Gobert (MIN) is already losing control of the rebound when Murray (SAC) reaches for the loose ball and marginal arm contact occurs.
